    <section toc="yes" anchor="iana" title="IANA Considerations">
      <t>
	This document recommends that IANA the zones listed in
	RFC6598 Zones to the "IPv4 Locally-Served DNS Zone" registry.
      </t>
    </section>
    <section toc="yes" anchor="security" title="Security Considerations">
      <t>
	As with any other Locally-Served DNS zone, reverse lookups
	of RFC6598 zones will require non-default configuration to
	return anything other than NXDOMAIN.
